arts.ttl: Rivals MK Dons and AFC Wimbledon share goalless stalemate
arts.sum: Chances were few and far between at Stadium MK.

arts.ttl: Milton Keynes Dons-AFC Wimbledon Statistical Preview
arts.sum: The Dons Derby takes place for the third time this season. Wimbledon have won their last three games against MK Dons. AFC Wimbledon have failed to win any of their six away Football League games agai...

arts.ttl: Milton Keynes boss wants side to use AFC Wimbledon clash to turn a corner in League Two campaign
arts.sum: Milton Keynes boss Scott Lindsey believes that tomorrow’s League Two clash against AFC Wimbledon is the perfect opportunity for his side to turn a corner this season. “I don’t want people to understand the importance of this game – I completely do.

arts.ttl: New Colchester United signing Jack Tucker on MK Dons switch
arts.sum: “Two clean sheets away from home is always a very positive thing “I’m looking forward to being part of a hopefully sold backline. “It’s a good opportunity for me; having spoken to the manager, he sold the club and everything about the place really well.

arts.ttl: Colchester United sign defender Jack Tucker from MK Dons
arts.sum: "He had some Premier League clubs looking at him, at that time - I remember going to a game and watched him play with Mark Robson at West Ham and I know they were interested in him, at the time. Tucker started his career at Gillingham, joining them at the age of seven years old.
